Package mil.navy.nrl.cmf.sousa.directory Description

sousa.directory is a collection of classes for implementing a directory service. It identifies the fields (DirectoryFields) that are present in the output of a directory service. It defines two ways to interact with a directory service: as an advertiser ( Advertiser) and as a consumer (ConsumerViewInterpreter).
